quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  7,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  7,1,"a, l-, m, s"
  7,2,"yeh aik kitaab hai jo tumhari taraf nazil ki gayi hai, pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tumahray dil mein is se koi jhijak nah ho is ke utaarnay ki gharz yeh hai ke tum is ke zaryay se (munkareenko ) daraoo aur imaan laane walay logon ko yaad dehani ho"
  7,3,"logo, jo kuch tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil kya gaya hai uss ki pairwi karo aur apne rab ko chore kar dosray srprston ki pairwi nah karo magar tum nasiyaat kam hi mantay ho"
  7,4,"kitni hi bastiyan hain jinhein hum ne halaak kar diya unn par hamara azaab achanak raat ke waqt toot para, ya din d_harhe aisay waqt aaya jab woh aaraam kar rahay thay"
  7,5,aur jab hamara azaab unn par aa gaya to un ki zabaan par iss ke siwa koi sada nah thi ke waqai hum zalim thay
  7,6,"pas yeh zaroor ho kar rehna hai ke hum unn logon se baz purse karen, jin ki taraf hum ne paighambar beje hain aur payghambaroon se bhi poucheen ( ke onhon ne pegham rasani ka farz kahan taq injaam diya aur inhen is ka kya jawab mila )"
  7,7,"phir hum khud poor y ilm ke sath sarguzisht un ke agay paish kar den ge, aakhir hum kahin gayab to nahi thay"
  7,8,aur wazan is roz ain haq hoga jin ke plrhe bhaari hon ge wohi Falah payen ge
  7,9,aur jin ke plrhe halkay rahen ge wohi apne aap ko khasaray mein mubtala karne walay hon ge kyunkay woh hamari ayaat ke sath zalimana bartao karte rahay thay
  7,10,"hum ne tumhen zameen mein ikhtiyarat ke sath basaayaa aur tumahray liye yahan samaan zeist faraham kya, magar tum log kam hi shukar guzaar hotay ho"
  7,11,"hum ne tumhari takhleeq ki ibtida ki, phir tumhari soorat banai, phir firshton se kaha aadam ko sajda karo is hukum par sab ne sajda kya magar iblees sajda karne walon mein shaamil nah howa"
  7,12,"poocha,"" tujhe kis cheez ne sajda karne se roka jab ke mein ne tujh ko hukum diya tha ?"" bola,"" mein uss se behtar hon, to ne mujhe aag se peda kya hai aur ussay matti se """
  7,13,"farmaya,"" acha to yahan se neechay utar tujhe haq nahi hai ke yahan barayi ka ghamand kere nikal ja ke Dur haqeeqat to un logon mein se hai jo khud apni zillat chahtay hain """
  7,14,"bola,"" mujhe uss din taq mohlat day jab ke yeh sab dobarah uthaye jayen ge """
  7,15,"farmaya,"" tujhe mohlat hai """
  7,16,"bola,"" acha to jis terhan to ne mujhe gumraahi mein mubtala kya mein bhi ab teri seedhi raah par"
  7,17,"inn insanon ki ghaat mein laga rahon ga, agay aur peechay, dayen aur baen, har taraf se inn ko ghayron ga aur to un mein se aksar ko shukar guzaar nah paye ga """
  7,18,"farmaya,"" nikal ja yahan se zaleel aur thukraya howa yaqeen rakh ke inn mein se jo teri pairwi karen ge, tujh sameit un sab se jahannum ko bhar dun ga"
  7,19,"aur ae aadam, to aur teri biwi, dono is jannat mein raho, jahan jis cheez ko tumhara jee chahay khao, magar is darakht ke paas nah phatakna warna zaalmon mein se ho jao ge """
  7,20,"phir shetan ne unn ko behkaya taakay un kisharmghain jo aik dosray se chhupayi gayi theen un ke samnay khol day is ne un se kaha,"" tumahray rab ne tumhe jo is darakht se roka hai is ki wajah iss ke siwa kuch nahi hai ke kahin tum farishtay nah ban jao, ya tumhe hameshgi ki zindagi haasil nah ho jaye"
  7,21,aur is ne qasam kha kar un se kaha ke mein tumhara sacha kher khuwa hon
  7,22,"is terhan dho ka day kar woh un dono ko rafta rafta apne dhab parlay aaya aakhir kaar jab unhon ne is darakht ka maza chakkha to un ke sattar aik dosray ke samnay khil gay aur apne jismon ko jannat ke pattoun se dhanknelagey tab un ke rab ne inhen puraka,"" kya mein ne tumhe is darakht se nah roka tha aur nah kaha tha ke shetan tumhara khula dushman hai? """
  7,23,"dono bol utthay,"" ae rab, hum ne apne oopar sitam kya, ab agar to ne hum se Dur guzar nah farmaya aur reham nah kya to yaqeenan hum tabah ho jayen ge """
  7,24,"farmaya,"" utar jao, tum aik dosray ke dushman ho, aur tumahray liye aik khaas muddat taq zameen hi mein jaye qarar aur samaan zeist hai """
  7,25,"aur farmaya,"" wahein tum ko jeena aur wahein marna hai aur isi mein se tum ko aakhir kaar nikala jaye ga """
  7,26,"ae aulaad aadam, hum ne tum par libaas nazil kya hai ke tumahray jism ke qabil sharam hisson ko dhanke aur tumahray liye jism ki hifazat aur zeenat ka zareya bhi ho, aur behtareen libaas taqwa ka libaas hai yeh Allah ki nshanyon mein se aik nishani hai, shayad ke log is se sabaq len"
  7,27,"ae bani aadam, aisa nah ho ke shetan tumhe phir usi terhan ftne mein mubtala kar day jis terhan is ne tumahray walidain ko jannat se nklwaya tha aur a noon ke libaas un par se utarwa diye thay taakay un kisharmghain aik dosray ke samnay khole woh aur is ke saathi tumhe aisi jagah se dekhte hain jahan se tum inhen nahi dekh satke inn shyatin ko hum ne unn logon ka sarparast bana diya hai jo imaan nahi laatay"
  7,28,yeh log jab koi sharamnaak kaam karte hain to kehte hain hum ne apne baap dada ko isi tareeqa par paaya hai aur Allah hi ne hamein aisa karne ka hukum diya hai inn se kaho Allah be hiyai ka hukum kabhi nahi diya karta kya tum Allah ka naam le kar woh baatein kehte ho jin ke mutaliq tumhe ilm nahi hai ( woh Allah ki taraf se hain ) ?
  7,29,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho, mere rab ne to raasti o insaaf ka hukum diya hai, aur is ka hukum to yeh hai ke har ibadat mein apna rukh theek rakho aur usi ko poukaro apne deen ko is ke liye khalis rakh kar jis terhan uss ne tumhe ab peda kya hai isi terhan tum phir peda kiye jao ge"
  7,30,"aik giroh koto is ne seedha rasta dikha diya hai, magar dosray giroh par gumraahi chaspan ho kar reh gayi hai, kyunkay unhon ne khuda ke bajaye shyatin ko apna sir parast bana liya hai aur woh samajh rahay hain ke hum seedhi raah par hain"
  7,31,"ae bani aadam, har ibadat ke mauqa par apni zeenat se aaraasta raho aur khao piyo aur hadd se tajawaz nah karo, Allah hadd se bherne walon ko pasand nahi karta"
  7,32,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho kis ne Allah ki uss zeenat ko haraam kar diya jisay Allah ne apne bundon ke liye nikala tha aur kis ne khuda ki bakhsh hui pak cheeze mamnoo kar den? kaho, yeh saari cheeze duniya ki zindagi mein bhi imaan laane walon ke liye hain, aur qayamat ke roz to khalstan unhi ke liye hon gi iss terhan hum apni baatein saaf saaf bayan karte hain unn logon ke liye jo ilm rakhnay walay hain"
  7,33,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho ke mere rab ne jo cheeze haraam ki hain woh to yeh hain : be sharmi ke kaam khuwa khulay hon ya chupay aur gunah aur haq ke khilaaf zayad-ti aur yeh ke Allah ke sath tum kisi ko shareek karo jis ke liye uss ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki aur yeh ke Allah ke naam par koi aisi baat kaho jis ke mutaliq tumhe ilm nah ho ke woh haqeeqat mein isi ne farmai hai"
  7,34,"har qoum ke liye mohlat ki aik muddat muqarrar hai, phir jab kisi qoum ki muddat aan poori hoti hai to aik gharri bhar ki takheer o taqdeem bhi nahi hoti"
  7,35,"( aur yeh baat Allah ne aaghaz takhleeq hi mein saaf farma di thi ke ) ae bani aadam, yaad rakho, agar tumahray paas khud tum hi mein se aisay rasool ayen jo tumhe meri ayaat suna rahay hon, to jo koi nafarmani se bachay ga aur apne rawayya ki islaah kar le ga is ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai"
  7,36,aur jo log hamari ayaat kojjhutlainge aur un ke muqaabla mein sar kashi barten ge wohi ahal dozakh hon ge jahan woh hamesha rahen ge
  7,37,"zahir hai ke uss se bara zalim aur ko noon ho ga jo bilkul jhooti baatein ghurr kar Allah ki taraf mansoob kere ya Allah ki sachhi ayaat kojhutla-ay aisay log apne noshta taqdeer ke mutabiq apna hissa paate rahen ge, yahan taq ke woh gharri aa jaye gi jab hamaray beje hue farishtay un ki roohein qabz karne ke liye pohnchain ge uss waqt woh unn se poucheen ge ke batao, ab kahan hain tumahray woh mabood jin ko tum ko khuda ke bajaye pkarte thay? woh kahin ge ke,"" sab hum se gum ho gay"" aur woh khud apne khilaaf gawahi den ge ke hum waqai munkir haq thay"
  7,38,"Allah farmaiye ga jao, tum bhi isi jahannum mein chalay jao jis mein tum se pehlay guzray hue giroh jin o ans ja chuke hain har giroh jab jahannum mein daakhil hoga to apne paish ro giroh par laanat karta howa daakhil hoga, hatta ke jab sab wahan jama ho jayen ge to har baad wala giroh pehlay giroh ke haq mein kahe ga ke ae rab, yeh log thay jinhon ne hum ko gumraah kya lehaza inhen aag ka dohra azaab day jawab mein irshad hoga, har aik ke liye dohra hi azaab hai magar tum jantay nahi ho"
  7,39,"aur pehla giroh dosray giroh se kahe ga ke ( agar hum qabil ilzaam thay ) to tumhi ko hum par konsi fazeelat haasil thi, ab apni kamaai ke nateeja mein azaab ka maza chako"
  7,40,"yaqeen jano, jin logon ne hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya hai aur un ke muqaabla mein sar kashi ki hai un ke liye aasman ke darwazay hargiz nah khole jayen ge unn ka jannat mein jana itna hi namumkin hai jitna soi ke nake se oont ka guzarna mujrimon ko hamaray haan aisa hi badla mila karta hai"
  7,41,un ke liye to jahannum ka bichona hoga aur jahannum hi ka odhna yeh hai woh jaza jo hum zaalmon ko diya karte hain
  7,42,bakhilaf is ke jin logon ne hamari ayaat ko maan liya hai aur achay kaam kiye hain aur is baab mein hum har aik ko is ki istetat hi ke mutabiq zimma- daar tehratay hain woh ahal jannat hain jahan woh hamesha rahen ge
  7,43,"un ke dilon mein aik dosray ke khilaaf jo kuch kudorat hogi usay hum nikaal den ge unn ke neechay nhrin behti hongi, aur woh kahin ge ke"" tareef khuda hi ke liye hai jis ne hamein yeh rasta dekhaya, hum khud raah nah pa satke thay agar khuda hamari rahnumai nah karta, hamaray rab ke beje hue rasool waqai haq hi le kar aeye thay"" uss waqt nida aeye gi ke"" yeh jannat jis ke tum waris banaye gay ho tumhe unn aamaal ke badlay mein mili hai jo tum karte rahay thay """
  7,44,"phir yeh jannat ke log dozakh walon se pukaar kar kahin ge,"" hum ne unn saaray wadon ko theek pa liya jo hamaray rab ne hum se kiye thay, kya tum ne bhi un wadon ko theek paaya jo tumahray rab ne kiye thay ?"" woh jawab den ge"" haan"" tab aik pukarnay wala un ke darmain pukare ga ke"" khuda ki laanat unn zaalmon par"
  7,45,"jo Allah ke rastay se logon ko roktay aur usay terha karna chahtay thay aur akhirat ke munkir thay """
  7,46,"un dono garohoon ke darmain aik oot haail hogi jis ki bulandiyon ( airaaf ) par kuch aur log hon ge yeh har aik ko is ke qiyafah se p_hchanin ge aur jannat walon se pukaar kar kahin ge ke"" salamti ho tum par"" yeh log jannat mein daakhil to nahi hue magar is ke umeed waar hunge"
  7,47,"aur jab un ki nigehain dozakh walon ki taraf phrin gi to kahin ge,"" ae rab! hamein inn zalim logon mein shaamil nah kejio """
  7,48,"phir yeh airaaf ke log dozakh ki chand barri barri shakhsiyation ko un ki alamton se pehchan kar pukaarain ge ke"" dekh liya tum ne, aaj nah tumahray jthe tumahray kisi kaam aeye aur nah woh saaz o samaan jin ko tum barri cheez samajte thay"
  7,49,"aur kya yeh ahal jannat wohi log nahi hain jin ke mutaliq tum kasmain kha kha kar kehte thay ke inn ko to khuda panni rehmat mein se kuch bhi nah day ga? aaj unhi se kaha gaya ke daakhil ho jao jannat mein, tumahray liye nah khauf hai nah ranj """
  7,50,"aur dozakh ke log jannat walon ko pukaarain ge ke kuch thora sa pani hum par daal do ya jo rizaq Allah ne tumhe diya hai usi mein se kuch pheink do woh jawab den ge ke"" Allah ne yeh dono cheeze unn munkareenhaq par haraam kar di hain"
  7,51,"jinhon ne apne deen ko khail aur tafreeh bana liya tha aur jinhein duniya ki zindagi ne fraib mein mubtala kar rakha tha Allah farmata hai ke aaj hum bhi inhen isi terhan bhala den ge jis terhan woh iss din ki mulaqaat ko bhoolay rahay aur hamari aayton ka inkaar karte rahay """
  7,52,hum inn logon ke paas aik aisi kitaab le aeye hain jis ko hum ne ilm ki bana par mufasil banaya hai aur jo imaan laane walon ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
  7,53,"ab kya yeh log iss ke siwa kisi aur baat ke muntazir hain ke woh injaam samnay aa jaye jis ki yeh kitaab khabar day rahi hai? jis roz woh injaam samnay aa gaya wohi log jinhon ne usay nazar andaaz kar diya tha kahin ge ke"" waqai hamaray rab ke rasool haq le kar aeye thay, phir kya ab hamein kuch safarishi milein ge jo hamaray haq mein sifarish karen? ya hamein dobarah wapas hi bhaij diya jaye taakay jo kuch hum pehlay karte thay is ke bajaye ab dosray tareeqay par kaam kar ke deikhein"" unhon ne apne aap ko khasaray mein daal diya aur woh saaray jhoot jo unhon ne tasneef kar rakhay thay aaj un se gum ho gay"
  7,54,"Dur haqeeqat tumhara rab Allah hi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko chay dinon mein peda kya, phir apne takhat saltanat par jalva farma howa jo raat ko din par dhaank deta hai aur phir din raat ke peechay dora chala aata hai jis ne Sooraj aur chaand aur tarre peda kiye sab is ke farmaan ke tabay hain khabardaar raho! usi ki Khalq hai aur isi ka amar hai bara ba barket hai Allah , saaray jahanon ka maalik o parvar-digaar"
  7,55,"a pannay rab ko poukaro girgrate hue aur chupkay chupkay, yaqeenan o hay hadd se guzarnay walon ko pasand nahi karta"
  7,56,"zameen mein fasaad barpaa nah karo jabkay is ki islaah ho chuki hai aur khuda hi ko poukaro khauf ke sath aur tama ke sath, yaqeenan Allah ki rehmat naik kirdaar logon se qareeb hai"
  7,57,"aur woh Allah hi hai jo hawaon ko apni rehmat ke agay agay khushkhabri liye hue bhejta hai, phir jab woh pani se lde hue baadal utha layte hain to inhen kisi murda sir zameen ki taraf harkat deta hai, aur wahan meen barsa kar ( usi meri hui zameen se ) terhan terhan ke phal nikaal lata hai dekho, is terhan hum mُrdon ko haalat mout se nikaltay hain, shayad ke tum is mushahiday se sabaq lau"
  7,58,jo zameen achi hoti hai woh apne rab ke hukum se khoob phal phool latayen hai aur jo zameen kharab hoti hai a seen se naaqis pedawar ke siwa kuch nahi nikalta is terhan hum nshanyon ko baar baar paish karte hain unn logon ke liye jo shukar guzaar honay walay hain
  7,59,"hum ne Nooh ko uss ki qoum ki taraf bheja is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, Allah ki bandagi karo, uss ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai mein tumahray haq mein aik holnaak din ke azaab se darta hon """
  7,60,"is ki qoum ke sardaro ne jawab diya"" hum ko to yeh nazar aata hai ke tum Sarih gumraahi mein mubtala ho """
  7,61,"Nooh ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, mein kisi gumraahi mein nahi para ho n balkay, mein rab alaalmin ka rasool hon"
  7,62,"tumhe apne rab ke paighamaat pohanchata hon, tumhara kher khuwa hon aur mujhe Allah ki taraf se woh kuch maloom hai jo tumhen maloom nahi hai"
  7,63,"kya tumhe is baat par taajjub howa ke tumahray paas khud tumhari apni qoum ke aik aadmi ke zareya se tumahray rab ki yaad dehani aayi taakay tumhe khabardaar kere aur tum ghalat rawi se bach jao aur tum par reham kya jaye? """
  7,64,"magar unhon ne is ko jhutla diya aakhir-kaar hum ne usay aur is ke sathiyon ko aik kashti mein nijaat di aur unn logon ko duubo diya jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya tha, yaqeenan woh andhay log thay"
  7,65,"aur Aad ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai hood ko bheja is ne kaha"" ae baradran قو m, Allah ki bandagi karo, uss ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai phir kya tum ghalat rawi se parhaiz nah karo ge? """
  7,66,"is ki qoum ke sardaro ne, jo is ki baat maan-ne se inkaar kar rahay thay, jawab mein kaha"" hum to tumhe be aqli mein mubtala samajte hain aur hamein gumaan hai ke tum jhutay ho """
  7,67,"is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, mein be aqli mein mubtala nahi hon balkay mein rab alaalmin ka rasool hon"
  7,68,"tum ko apne rab ke paighamaat pohanchata hon, aur tumhara aisa kher khuwa hon jis par bharosa kya ja sakta hai"
  7,69,"kya tumhe is baat par taajjub howa ke tumahray paas khud tumhari apni qoum ke aik aadmi ke zareya se tumahray rab ki yaad dehani aayi taakay woh tumhen khabardaar kere? bhool nah jao ke tumahray rab ne Nooh ki qoum ke baad tum ko uss ka janasheen banaya aur tumhe khoob tano mand kya, pas Allah ki qudrat ke karishmo ko yaad rakho, umeed hai ke Falah pao ge """
  7,70,"unhon ne jawab diya"" kya to hamaray paas is liye aaya hai ke hum akailey Allah hi ki ibadat karen aur unhen chore den jin ki ibadat hamaray baap dada karte aeye hain? acha to le aa woh azaab jis ki to hamein dhamki deta hai agar to sacha hai """
  7,71,"is ne kaha"" tumahray rab ki phatkaar tum par par gayi aur is ka ghazab toot para kya tum mujh se unn naamon par jhagarte ho jo tum ne aur tumahray baap dada ne rakh liye hain, jin ke liye Allah ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki hai acha to tum bhi intzaar karo aur mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon """
  7,72,aakhir-kaar hum ne apni meharbani se hood aur is ke sathiyon ko bacha liya aur unn logon ki jarr kaat di jo hamari ayaat ko jhutla chuke thay aur imaan laane walay nah thay
  7,73,"aur smod ki taraf hum ne unn ke bhai saleh ko bheja is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, Allah ki bandagi karo, is ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai tumahray paas tumahray rab ki khuli Daleel aa gayi hai yeh Allah ki oontni tumahray liye aik nishani ke tor par hai, lehaza usay chore do ke khuda ki zameen mein chrti phiray is ko kisi buray iraday se haath nah lagana warna aik dard naak azaab tumhe aa le ga"
  7,74,"yaad karo woh waqt jab Allah ne qoum Aad ke baad tumhe is ka janasheen banaya aur tum ko zameen mein yeh manzilat bakhsh ke tum uss ke hamwar mahdanon mein aliiiii shaan mehal banatay aur is ke pahoron ko makanaat ki shakal mein tarashtain ho pas is ki qudrat ke karishmo se ghaafil nah ho jao aur zameen mein fasaad barpaa nah karo """
  7,75,"uss ki qoum ke sardaro ne jo barray banay hue thay, kamzor tabqa ke unn logon se jo imaan le aeye thay kaha"" kya tum waqai yeh jantay ho ke saleh apne rab ka paighambar hai ?"" unhon ne jawab diya"" be shak jis pegham ke sath woh bheja gaya hai ussay hum mantay hain """
  7,76,"unn buraiee ke mdayon ne kaha jis cheez ko tum ne maana hai hum is ke munkir hain """
  7,77,"phir unhon ne is oontni ko maar dala aur poooray tamarad ke sath apne rab ke hukum ki khilaaf warzi kar guzray, aur saleh se keh diya ke le aa woh azaab jis ki to hamein dhamki deta hai agar to waqai payghambaroon mein se hai"
  7,78,aakhir ka ray aik dhula dainay wali aafat ne unhen aa liya aur woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre ke parre reh gay
  7,79,"aur saleh yeh kehta howa un ki bustiyon se nikal gaya ke"" ae meri qoum, mein ne apne rab ka pegham tujhe pouncha diya aur mein ne teri bohat kher khawahi ki, magar mein kya karoon ke tujhe apne kher khuwa pasand hi nahi hain """
  7,80,"aur loot ko hum ne paighambar bana kar bheja, phir yaad karo jab uss ne apni qoum se kaha"" kya tum aisay be haya ho gay ho, ke woh fehash kaam karte ho jo tum se pehlay duniya mein kisi ne nahi kya ?"
  7,81,"tum aurton ko chore kar mardon se apni khwahish poori karte ho haqeeqat yeh hai ke tum bilkul hi hadd se guzar jaane walay log ho """
  7,82,"magar is ki qoum ka jawab is ke siwa kuch nah tha ke"" nikalu inn logon ko apni bustiyon se, barray pakbaaz bantay hain yeh """
  7,83,aakhir-kaar hum ne loot aur iss ke ghar walon ko bajuz is ki biwi ke jo peechay reh jaane walon mein thi
  7,84,"bacha kar nikaal diya aur is qoum par brsayi aik barish, phir dekho ke unn mujrimon ka kya injaam howa"
  7,85,"aur Mudin walon ki taraf hum ne un ke bhai Shoiab ko bheja is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, Allah ki bandagi karo, uss ke siwa tumhara koi khuda nahi hai tumahray paas tumahray rab ki saaf rahnumai aa gayi hai, lehaza wazan aur pemanay poooray karo, logon ko unn ki cheezon mein ghata nah do, aur zameen mein fasaad barpaa nah karo jab ke is ki islaah ho chuki hai, isi mein tumhari bhalai hai agar tum waqai momin ho"
  7,86,"aur ( zindagi ke ) har rastay par rehzan ban kar nah baith jao ke logon ko khauf zada karne aur imaan laane walon ko khuda ke rastay se roknay lagu aur seedhi raah ko terha karne ke darpay ho jao yaad karo woh zamana jabkay tum thoray thay phir Allah ne tumhe bohat kar diya, aur ankhen khol kar dekho ke duniya mein mfsdon ka kya injaam howa hai"
  7,87,"agar tum mein se aik giroh is taleem par jis ke sath mein bheja gaya hon, imaan lata hai aur dosra imaan nahi lata, to sabr ke sath dekhte raho yahan taq ke Allah hamaray darmain faisla kar day, aur wohi sab se behtar faisla karne wala hai """
  7,88,"is ki qoum ke sardaro ne, jo apni barayi ke ghamand mein mubtala thay, a seen se kaha ke"" ae Shoiab, hum tujhe aur unn logon ko jo tairay sath imaan laaye hain apni bastii se nikaal den ge warna tum logon ko hamari millat mein wapas aana hoga"" Shoiab ne jawab diya"" kya zabardasti hamein phera jaye ga khuwa hum raazi nah hon ?"
  7,89,"hum Allah par jhoot gharnay walay hon ge agar tumhari millat mein palat ayen jabkay Allah hamein is se nijaat day chuka hai hamaray liye to is ki taraf palatna ab kisi terhan mumkin nahi ila yeh ke khuda hamara rab hi aisa chahay hamaray rab ka ilm har cheez par haawi hai, usi par hum ne aetmaad kar liya ae rab, hamaray aur hamari qoum ke darmain theek theek faisla kar day aur to behtareen faisla karne wala hai """
  7,90,"is ki qoum ke sardaro ne, jo is ki baat maan-ne se inkaar kar chuke thay, aapas mein kaha"" agar tum ne Shoiab ki pairwi qubool kar li to barbaad ho jao ge """
  7,91,magar howa yeh ke aik dhula dainay wali aafat ne unn ko aa liya aur woh apne gharon mein avndhe parre ke parre reh gay
  7,92,jin logon ne Shoiab ko jhtlaya woh aisay mite ke goya kabhi un gharon mein basey hi nah thay Shoiab ke jhutlanay walay hi aakhir-kaar barbaad ho kar rahay
  7,93,"aur Shoiab yeh keh kar un ki bustiyon se nikal gaya ke"" ae baradran qoum, mein ne apne rab ke paighamaat tumhe pouncha diye aur tumhari kher khawahi ka haq ada kar diya ab mein uss qoum par kaisay afsos karoon jo qubool haq se inkaar karti hai """
  7,94,kabhi aisa nahi howa ke hum ne kisi bastii mein nabi bheja ho aur uss bastii ke logon ko pehlay tangi aur sakhti mein mubtala nah kya ho is khayaal se ke shayad woh aajzi par utar ayen
  7,95,"phir hum ne un ki badhaali ko khush haali se badal diya yahan taq ke woh khoob phalay phoolay aur kehnay lagey ke"" hamaray islaaf par bhi achay aur buray din atay hi rahay hain"" aakhir-kaar hum ne inhen achanak pakar liya aur inhen khabar taq nah hui"
  7,96,"agar bustiyon ke log imaan laatay aur taqwa ki rawish ikhtiyar karte to hum un par aasman aur zameen se barkatoon ke darwazay kho l- dete, magar onhon ne to jhtlaya, lehaza hum ne uss buri kamaai ke hisaab mein inhen pakar liya jo woh samaitt rahay thay"
  7,97,phir kya bustiyon ke log ab is se be khauf ho gay hain ke hamari girift kabhi achanak unn par raat ke waqt nah aa jaye gi jab ke woh sotay parre hon ?
  7,98,ya inhen itminan ho gaya hai ke hamara mazboot haath kabhi yakayak un par din ke waqt nah parre ga jab ke woh khail rahay hon ?
  7,99,kya yeh log Allah ki chaal se be khauf hain? halaank Allah ki chaal se wohi qoum be khauf hoti hai jo tabah honay wali ho
  7,100,"aur kya unn logon ko jo sabiq ahal zameen ke baad zameen ke waris hotay hain, iss amar waqai ne kuch sabaq nahi diya ke agar hum chahain to un keKasoroo-n par inhen pakar satke hain? ( magar woh sabaq amooz haqayiq se taghaful brtte hain ) aur hum un ke dilon par mohar laga dete hain, phir woh kuch nahi suntay"
  7,101,"yeh qoumain jin ke qissay hum tumhe suna rahay hain ( tumahray samnay misaal mein mojood hain ) un ke rasool un ke pa seen khuli khuli nishanain le kar aeye, magar jis cheez ko woh aik dafaa jhutla chuke thay phir ussay woh maan-ne walay nah thay dekho is terhan hum munkareen haq ke dilon par mohar laga dete hain"
  7,102,hum ne un mein se aksar mein koi paas ehad nah paaya balkay aksar ko fasik hi paaya
  7,103,"phir unn qomon ke baad ( jin ka zikar oopar kya gaya ) hum ne moose ko apni nshanyon ke sath firaon aur is ki qoum ke sardaro ke paas bheja magar unhon ne bhi hamari nshanyon ke sath zulm kya, pas dekho ke un mfsdon ka kya injaam howa"
  7,104,"moose ne kaha"" ae firaon, mein kaayenaat ke maalik ki taraf se bheja howa aaya ho n"
  7,105,"mera mansab yahi hai ke Allah ka naam le kar koi baat haq ke siwa nah kahoon, mein tum logon ke paas tumahray rab ki taraf se Sarih Daleel ماموریت le kar aaya hon, lehaza to bani Israel ko mere sath bhaij day """
  7,106,"firaon ne kaha"" agar to koi nishani laya hai aur apne daaway mein sacha hai to usay paish kar """
  7,107,moose ne apna asa phenka aur yaka yak woh aik jeeta jaagta اsdha tha
  7,108,is ne apni jaib se haath nikala aur sab dekhnay walon ke samnay woh chamak raha tha
  7,109,"a seen par firaon ki qoum ke sardaro ne aapas mein kaha ke"" yaqeenan yeh shakhs bara maahir jaadoo gir hai"
  7,110,"tumhe tumhari zameen se be dakhal karna chahta hai, ab kaho kya kehte ho? """
  7,111,phir unn sab ne firaon ko mahswara diya ke usay aur is ke bhai ko intzaar mein rakhiye aur tamam shehron mein hrkare bhaij degiye
  7,112,ke har maahir fun jadugar ko aap ke paas le ayen
  7,113,"chunancha jadugar firaon ke paas aa gay onhon ne"" agar hum ghalib rahay to hamein is ka sila to zaroor miley ga? """
  7,114,"firaon ne jawab diya"" haan, aur tum Maqarrab bargaah ho ge """
  7,115,"phir onhon ne moose se kaha"" tum phenkhte ho ya hum phinkin? """
  7,116,"moose ne jawab diya"" tum hi phenko"" unhon ne jo apne Aanchar phainky to nigahon ko mashooor aur dilon ko khauf zada kar diya aur bara hi zabardast jaadoo bana laaye"
  7,117,hum ne moose ko ishara kya ke pheink apna asa is ka phenkna tha ke aan ki aan mein woh un ke is jhutay tilsam ko nglta chala gaya
  7,118,is terhan jo haq tha woh haq saabit howa aur jo kuch onhon ne bana rakha tha woh baatil ho kar reh gaya
  7,119,firaon aur is ke saathi maidan muqaabla mein maghloob hue aur ( fatah mand honay ke bajaye ) ultay zaleel ho gay
  7,120,aurjadogaron ka haal yeh howa ke goya kisi cheez ne andar se inhen sjday mein gira diya
  7,121,"kehnay lagey"" hum ne maan liya rab alaalmin ko"
  7,122,"uss rab ko jisay moose aur haroon mantay hain """
  7,123,"firaon ne kaha"" tum is par imaan le aeye qabal is ke ke mein tumhe ijazat dun? yaqeenan yeh koi khufia saaz sh thi jo tum logon ne is darul-saltnat mein ki taakay is ke malikon ko Iqtidaar se be dakhal kar do acha tawa seen ka nateeja ab tumhe maloom howa jata hai"
  7,124,"mein tumahray haath paon mukhalif simtao se ktwa dun ga aur is ke baad tum sab ko suli par churaho-n ga """
  7,125,"unhon ne jawab diya"" bahar haal hamein palatna apne rab hi ki taraf hai"
  7,126,"to jis baat par hum se intiqam lena chahta hai woh iss ke siwa kuch nahi ke hamaray rab ki nishanain jab hamaray samnay aa gayeen to hum ne inhen maan liya ae rab, hum par sabr ka Faizan kar aur hamein duniya se utha to iss haal mein ke hum tairay farmaa bardaar hon """
  7,127,"firaon se uss ki qoum ke sardaro ne kaha"" kya to moose aur uss ki qoum ko yuhin chore day ga ke malik mein fasaad philayin aur woh teri aur tairay mabodon ki bandagi chore baithy ?"" firaon ne jawab diya"" mein unn ke beiton ko qatal kraon ga aur unn ki aurton ko jeeta rehne dun ga hamaray Iqtidaar ki girift un par mazboot hai """
  7,128,"moose ne apni qoum se kaha"" Allah se madad mango aur sabr karo, zameen Allah ki hai, apne bundon mein se jis ko chahta hai is ka waris bana deta hai, aur aakhri kamyabi unhi ke liye jo is se drtay hue kaam karen """
  7,129,"is ki qoum ke logon ne kaha"" tairay anay se pehlay bhi hum sataye jatay thay aur ab tairay anay par bhi sataye ja rahay hain"" is ne jawab diya"" qareeb hai woh waqt ke tumhara rab tumahray dushman ko halaak kar day aur tum ko zameen mein khalifa banaye, phir dekhe ke tum kaisay amal karte ho """
  7,130,hum ne firaon ke logon ko kayi saal taq qeht aur pedawar ki kami mein mubtala rakha ke shayad un ko hosh aeye
  7,131,"magar unn ka haal yeh tha ke jab acha zamana aata to kehte ke hum isi ke mustahiq hain, aur jab bura zamana aata to moose aur is ke sathiyon ko apne liye faal -e-badtehratay, halaank Dur haqeeqat un ki faal bad to Allah ke paas thi, magar un mein se aksar be ilm thay"
  7,132,"unhon ne moose se kaha ke"" to hamein mashooor karne ke liye khuwa koi nishani le aeye, hum to teri baat maan-ne walay nahi hain """
  7,133,"aakhir-kaar hum ne un par tufaan bheja, tiddi dil chhorey,sursuryan philayin, maindak nikalay, aur khoo noon barsaya yeh sab nishanain allag allag kar ke deikhein, magar woh sir kashi kiye chalay gay aur woh barray hi mujrim log thay"
  7,134,"jab kabhi unn par bulaa nazil ho jati to kehte"" ae moose, tujhe apne rab ki taraf se jo mansab haasil hai is ki bana par hamaray haq mein dua kar, agar ab ke to hum par se yeh bulaa Talwa day to hum teri baat maan len ge aur bani Israel ko tairay sath bhaij den ge """
  7,135,"magar jab hum un par se apna azaab aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye, jis ko woh behar haal pounchanay walay thay, hata letay to woh yklkht apne ehad se phir jatay"
  7,136,tab hum ne unn se intiqam liya aur inhen samandar mein ghark kar diya kyunkay unhon ne hamari nshanyon ko jhtlaya tha aur unn se be parwa ho gay thay
  7,137,"aur unn ki jagah hum ne unn logon ko jo kamzor bana kar rakhay gay thay, uss sarzamen ke mashriq o maghrib ka waris bana diya jisay hum ne barkatoon se malaa maal kya tha is terhan bani Israel ke haq mein tairay rab ka wada kher poora howa kyunkay onhon ne sabr se kaam liya tha aur firaon aur is ki qoum ka woh sab kuch barbaad kar diya gaya jo woh banatay aur charhatay thay"
  7,138,"bani Israel ko hum ne samandar se guzaar diya, phir woh chalay aur rastay mein aik aisi qoum par unn ka guzar howa jo apne chand buton ki garweedah bani hui thi kehnay lagey,"" ae moose, hamaray liye bhi koi aisa mabood bana day jaisay inn logon ke mabood hain"" moose ne kaha"" tum log barri nadani ki baatein karte ho"
  7,139,"yeh log jis tareeqa ki pairwi kar rahay hain woh to barbaad honay wala hai aur jo amal woh kar rahay hain woh sara sar baatil hai """
  7,140,"phir moose ne kaha"" kya mein Allah ke siwa koi aur mabood tumahray liye talaash karoon? halaank woh Allah hi hai jis ne tumhe duniya bhar ki qomon par fazeelat bakhsh hai"
  7,141,"aur ( Allah farmata hai ) woh waqt yaad karo jab hum ne firaon walon se tumhe nijaat di jin ka haal yeh tha ke tumhe sakht azaab mein mubtala rakhtay thay, tumahray beiton ko qatal karte aur tumhari aurton ko zindah rehne dete thay aur is mein tumahray rab ki taraf se tumhari barri azmaish thi"
  7,142,"hum ne moose ko tees shab o roz ke liye ( koh seena par ) talab kya aur baad mein das din ka aur izafah kar diya, iss terhan uss ke rab ki muqarrar kardah muddat poooray chalees din ho gayi moose ne chaltay hue apne bhai haroon se kaha ke"" mere peechay tum meri qoum mein meri janshini karna aur theek kaam karte rehna aur bigaar peda karne walon ke tareeqay par nah chalna """
  7,143,"jab woh hamaray muqarrar kiye hue waqt par pouncha aur is ke rab ne is se kalaam kya to is ne iltija ki ke"" ae rab, mujhe ya-ra-ay nazar day ke mein tujhe daikhon"" farmaya"" to mujhe nahi dekh sakta haan zara samnay ke pahar ki taraf dekh, agar woh apni jagah qaim reh jaye to Albata to mujhe dekh sakay ga"" chunancha is ke rab ne jab pahar par tajallii ki to usay rezah rezah kar diya aur moose ghash kha kar gir para jab hosh aaya to bola"" pak hai teri zaat, mein tairay huzoor tauba karta hon aur sab se pehla imaan laane wala mein hon """
  7,144,"farmaya"" ae moose, mein ne tamam logon par tarjeeh day kar tujhe muntakhib kya ke Meer y paigambri kere aur mujh se hum kalaam ho pas jo kuch mein tujhe dun usay le aur shukar jbaja laa"""
  7,145,"is ke baad hum ne moose ko har shoba zindagi ke mutaliq nasiyaat aur har pehlu ke mutaliq wazeh hadaayat tkhtyon par likh kar day di aur is se kaha :"" inn Hadayat ko mazboot hathon se sambhaal aur apni qoum ko hukum day ke un ke behtar mafhuum ki pairwi karen anqareeb mein tumhe فاسقوں ke ghar dukhao ga"
  7,146,"mein apni nshanyon se unn logon ki nigehain phair dun ga jo baghair kisi haq ke zameen mein barray bantay hain, woh khuwa koi nishani dekh len kabhi is par imaan nah layein ge, agar seedha rasta unn ke samnay aeye to usay ikhtiyar nah karen ge aur agar tehraa rasta nazar aeye to is par chal parrin ge, is liye ke unhon ne hamari nshanyon ko jhtlaya aur un se be parwai karte rahay"
  7,147,"hamari nshanyon ko jis kisi ne jhtlaya aur akhirat ki paishi ka inkaar kya uss ke saaray aamaal zaya ho gay kya log iss ke siwa kuch aur jaza pa satke hain ke jaissa karen waisa bharain? """
  7,148,moose ke peechay is ki qoum ke logon ne apne zewaro-n se aik bichhre ka patla bana liya jis mein se bail ki si aawaz nikalti thi kya unhen nazar nah aata tha ke woh nah un se boltaa hai nah kisi maamla mein un ki rahnumai karta hai? magar phir bhi onhon ne usay mabood bana liya aur woh sakht zalim thay
  7,149,"phir jab un ki fraib khordghi ka tilsam toot gaya o ray onhon ne dekh liya ke Dur haqeeqat woh gumraah ho gay hain to kehnay lagey ke"" agar hamaray rab ne hum par reham nah farmaya aur hum se dar guzar nah kya to hum barbaad ho jayen ge """
  7,150,"idhar se moose ghusse aur ranj mein bhara howa apni qoum ki taraf palta atay hi is ne kaha"" bohat buri janshini ki tum logon ne mere baad! kya tum se itna sabr nah howa ke apne rab ke hukum ka intzaar kar letay ?"" aur tkhtyan pheink den aur apne bha yi ( haroon ) ke sir ke baal pakar kar usay khincha haroon ne kaha"" ae meri maa ke betay, inn logon ne mujhe daba liya aur qareeb tha ke mujhe maar daaltay pas to dushmanon ko mujh par hansnay ka mauqa nah day aur is zalim giroh ke sath mujhe nah shaamil kar """
  7,151,"tab moose ne kaha"" ae rab, mujhe aur mere bhai ko maaf kar aur hamein apni rehmat mein daakhil farma, to sab se barh kar Raheem hai """
  7,152,"( jawab mein irshad howa ke )"" jin logon ne bichhre ko mabood banaya woh zaroor apne rab ke ghazab mein girftar ho kar rahen ge aur duniya ki zindagi mein zaleel hon ge jhoot gharnay walon ko hum aisi hi saza dete hain"
  7,153,"aur jo log buray amal karen phir tauba kar len aur imaan le ayen to yaqeenan iss tauba o imaan ke baad tera rab dar guzar aur reham frmane wala hai """
  7,154,phir jab moose ka gussa thanda howa to is ne woh tkhtyan utha len jin ki tehreer mein hadaayat aur rehmat thi unn logon ke liye jo apne rab se drtay hain
  7,155,"aur uss ne apni qoum ke sattar admion ko muntakhib kya taakay woh ( uss ke sath ) hamaray muqarrar kiye hue waqt par haazir hon jab inn logon ko aik sakht zalzalay ne aa pakra to moose ne arz kya"" ae mere sarkar, aap chahtay to pehlay hi inn ko aur mujhe halaak kar saktay thay kya aap uss qasoor mein jo hum mein se chand nadano-n ne kiya tha hum sab ko halaak kar den ge? yeh to aap ki daali hui aik azmaish thi jis ke zareya se aap jisay chahtay hain gumraahi mein mubtala kar dete hain aur jisay chahtay hain hadaayat bakhash dete hain hamaray sir parast to aap hi hain pas hamein maaf kar degiye aur hum par reham frmayie, aap sab se barh kar maaf frmane walay hain"
  7,156,"aur hamaray liye is duniya ki bhalai bhi likh degiye aur akhirat ki bhi, hum ne aap ki taraf rujoo kar liya"" jawab mein irshad howa"" saza to mein jisay chahta hon deta hon, magar meri rehmat har cheez par chhai hui hai, aur ussay mein unn logon ke haq mein likhon ga jo nafarmani se parhaiz karen ge, zkoh den ge aur meri ayaat par imaan layein ge """
  7,157,"( pas aaj yeh rehmat unn logon ka hissa hai ) jo iss paighambar, nabi ammi ki pairwi ikhtiyar karen jis ka zikar unhen apne haan torat aur injeel mein likha howa milta hai woh inhen neki ka hukum deta hai, badi se rokta hai, un ke liye pak cheeze halal o ray napak cheeze haraam karta hai, aur un par se woh boojh atarta hai jo unn par lde hue thay aur woh bandishen kholta hai jin mein woh jakray hue thay lehaza jo log is par imaan layein aur is ki himayat aur nusrat karen aur uss roshni ki pairwi ikhtiyar karen jo is ke sath nazil ki gayi hai, wohi Falah panay walay hain"
  7,158,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, kaho ke"" aeInsano mein tum sab ki taraf uss khuda ka paighambar hon jo zameen aur asmano ki badshahi ka maalik hai, uss ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai, wohi zindagi bkhshta hai aur wohi mout deta hai, pas imaan lao Allah par aur is ke beje hue nabi ammi par jo Allah aur is ke arshadat ko maanta hai, aur pairwi ikhtiyar karo uss ki, umeed hai ke tum raah raast pa lau ge """
  7,159,moose ki qoum mein aik giroh aisa bhi tha jo haq ke mutabiq hadaayat karta aur haq hi ke mutabiq insaaf karta tha
  7,160,aur hum ne is qoum ko baara ghranon mein taqseem kar ke inhen mustaqil garohoon ki shakal day di thi aur jab moose se is ki qoum ne pani manga to hum ne is ko ishara kya ke falan chattaan par apni laathi maro chunancha is chattaan se yakayak baara chashmay phoot niklay aur har giroh ne apne pani lainay ki jagah mutayyan kar li hum ne unn par baadal ka saya kya aur unn par mann o salwa utaara khao woh pak cheeze jo hum ne tum ko bakhsh hain magar is ke baad unhon ne jo kuch kya to hum par zulm nahi kya balkay aap apne hi oopar zulm karte rahay
  7,161,"yaad karo woh waqt jab un se kaha gaya tha ke iss bastii mein ja kar bas jao aur is ki pedawar se hasb Mansha rozi haasil karo aur حطہ حطہ kehte jao aur shehar ke darwazay mein sajda raiz hotay hue daakhil ho, hum tumhari khataien maaf karen ge aur naik rawayya rakhnay walon ko mazeed fazl se nawaazain ge """
  7,162,"magar jo log unn mein se zalim thay onhon ne uss baat ko jo unn se kahi gayi thi badal dala, aur nateeja yeh howa ke hum ne un ke zulm ki Padaash mein un par aasman se azaab bhaij diya"
  7,163,aur zara inn se aُ seen bastii ka haal bhi pucho jo samandar ke kinare waqay thi aِnhin yaad dlao woh waqea ke wahan ke log sabt ( hafta ) ke din ehkaam Ellahi ki khilaaf warzi karte thay aur yeh ke machhliyan sabt hi ke din ubhar ubhar kar satah par unn ke samnay aati theen aur sabt ke siwa baqi dinon mein nahi aati theen yeh is liye hota tha ke hum un ki nafarmanio-n ki wajah se un ko azmaish mein daal rahay thay
  7,164,"aur inhen yeh bhi yaad lao ke jab unn mein se aik giroh ne dosray giroh se kaha tha ke"" tum aisay logon ko kyun nasiyaat karte ho jinhein Allah halaak karne wala ya sakht saza dainay wala hai"" to unhon ne jawab diya tha ke"" hum yeh sab kuch tumahray rab ke huzoor apni moazrat paish karne ke liye karte hain aur is umeed par karte hain ke shayad yeh log is ki nafarmani se parhaiz karne lagen """
  7,165,Aakhir -e- Kar woh unn Hadayat ko bilkul hi faramosh kar gay jo inhen yaad karai gayi theen to hum ne unn logon ko bacha liya jo buraiee se roktay thay aur baqi sab logon ko jo zalim thay un ki nafarmanio-n par sakht azaab mein pakar liya
  7,166,"phir jab woh poori sar kashi ke sath wohi kaam kiye chalay gay jis se inhen roka gaya tha, to hum ne kaha ke bandar ho jao zaleel aur khawar"
  7,167,"aur yaad karo jabkay tumahray rab ne elaan kar diya ke"" woh qayamat taq barabar aisay log bani Israel par musallat karta rahay ga jo un ko bad tareen azaab den ge,"" yaqeenan tumhara rab saza dainay mein taiz dast hai aur yaqeenan woh Dur guzar aur reham se bhi kaam lainay wala hai"
  7,168,hum ne un ko zameen mein tukre tukre kar ke bohat si qomon mein taqseem kar diya kuch log un mein naik thay aur kuch a seen se mukhtalif aur hum un ko achay aur buray halaat se azmaish mein mubtala karte rahay ke shayad yeh palat ayen
  7,169,"phir agli naslon ke baad aisay na Khalf log un ke janasheen hue jo kitaab Ellahi ke waris ho kar isi dunyae Danni ke faiday samettay hain aur keh dete hain ke tawaqqa hai hamein maaf kar diya jaye ga, aur agar wohi mata duniya phir samnay aati hai to phir lapak kar usay le letay hain kya un se kitaab ka ehad nahi liya ja chuka hai ke Allah ke naam par wohi baat kahin jo haq ho? aur yeh khud parh chuke hain jo kitaab mein likha hai akhirat ki qiyam gaah to khuda taras logon ke liye hi behtar hai, kya tum itni si baat nahi samajte ?"
  7,170,"jo log kitaab ki pabandi kar te hain aur jinhon ne namaz qaim rakhi hai, yaqeenan aisay naik kirdaar logon ka ajar hum zaya nahi karen ge"
  7,171,"inhen woh waqt bhi kuch yaad hai jabkay hum ne pahar ko hila kar un par is terhan chhaa diya tha ke goya woh chhatri hai aur yeh gumaan kar rahay thay ke woh un par aa parre ga aur uss waqt hum ne un se kaha tha ke jo kitaab hum tumhe day rahay hain usay mazbooti ke sath thamo aur jo kuch is mein likha hai usay yaad rakho, tawaqqa hai ke tum ghalat rawi se bachay raho ge"
  7,172,"aur ae nabi, logon ko yaad dlao woh waqt jabkay tumahray rab ne bani aadam ki pshton se un ki nasal ko nikala tha aur inhen khud un ke oopar gawah banatay hue poocha tha"" kya mein tumhara rab nahi hon ?"" unhon ne kaha"" zaroor aap hi hamaray rab hain, hum is par gawahi dete hain"" yeh hum ne is liye kya ke kahin tum qayamat ke roz yeh nah keh do ke"" hum to is baat se be khabar thay, """
  7,173,"ya yeh nah kehnay lagu ke"" shirk ki ibtida to hamaray baap dada ne hum se pehlay ki thi aur hum baad ko un ki nasal se peda hue, phir kya aap hamein uss qasoor mein pakarte hain jo ghalat car logon ne kya tha """
  7,174,"dekho, iss terhan hum nishanain wazeh tor par paish karte hain aur is liye karte hain ke yeh log palat ayen"
  7,175,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn ke samnay uss shakhs ka haal bayan karo jis ko hum ne apni ayaat ka ilm ataa kya tha magar woh un ki pabandi se nikal bhaga aakhir kaar shetan is ke peechay par gaya yahan taq ke woh bhatakne walon mein shaamil ho kar raha"
  7,176,"agar hum chahtay to usay unn aayton ke zareya se bulandi ataa karte, magar woh to zameen hi ki taraf jhuk kar reh gaya aur apni khwahish nafs hi ke peechay para raha, lehaza is ki haalat kuttay ki si ho gayi ke tum is par hamla karo tab bhi zabaan latakaye rahay aur usay chore do tab bhi zabaan latakaye rahay yahi misaal hai unn logon ki jo hamari ayaat ko jutlatay hain tum yeh hakayaat inn ko sunaate raho, shayad ke yeh kuch ghhor o fikar karen"
  7,177,"barri hi buri misaal hai aisay logon ki jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya, aur woh aap apne hi oopar zulm karte rahay hain"
  7,178,jisay Allah hadaayat bakhshay bas wohi raah raast paata hai aur jis ko Allah apni rahnumai se mahroom kar day wohi nakaam o namuraad ho kar rehta hai
  7,179,"aur yeh haqeeqat hai ke bohat se jin aur ensaan aisay hain jin ko hum ne jahannum hi ke liye peda kya hai un ke paas dil hain magar woh un se sochte nahi un ke paas ankhen hain magar woh un se dekhte nahi un ke paas kaan hain magar woh un se suntay nahi woh janwaron ki terhan hain balkay un se bhi ziyada gay guzray, yeh woh log hain jo ghaflat mein kho ye gay hain"
  7,180,"Allah achay naamon ka mustahiq hai, is ko achay hi naamon se poukaro aur unn logon ko chore do jo is ke naam rakhnay mein raasti se munharif ho jatay hain jo kuch woh karte rahay hain is ka badla woh paker rahen ge"
  7,181,hamari makhlooq mein aik giroh aisa bhi hai jo theek theek haq ke mutabiq hadaayat aur haq hi ke mutabiq insaaf karta hai
  7,182,"rahay woh log jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhutla diya hai, to inhen hum batadreej aisay tareeqa se tabahi ki taraf le jayen ge ke inhen khabar taq nah hogi"
  7,183,"mein un ko dheel day raha hon, meri chaal ka koi toar nahi hai"
  7,184,aur kya inn logon ne kabhi socha nahi? inn ke Rafeeq par junoon ka koi assar nahi hai woh to aik khabardaar hai jo ( bura injaam samnay anay se pehlay ) saaf saaf mutnabba kar raha hai
  7,185,kya un logon ne aasman o zameen ke intizam par kabhi ghhor nahi kya aur kisi cheez ko bhi jo khuda ne peda ki hai ankhen khol kar nahi dekha? aur kya yeh bhi unhon ne nahi socha ke shayad inn ki mohlat zindagi poori honay ka waqt qareeb aa laga ho? phir aakhirPeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamki iss tanbeeh ke baad aur konsi baat aisi ho sakti hai jis par yeh imaan layein ?
  7,186,"jis ko Allah rahnumai se mahroom kar day uss ke liye phir koi rehnuma nahi hai, aur Allah aِnhin inn ki sar kashi hi mein bhatakta howa chhorey deta hai"
  7,187,"yeh log tum se puchhte hain ke aakhir woh qayamat ki gharri kab nazil hogi? kaho"" is ka ilm mere rab hi ke paas hai ussay apne waqt par wohi zahir kere ga asmano aur zameen mein woh bara sakht waqt hoga woh tum par achanak aa jaye ga"" yeh log is ke mutaliq tum se is terhan puchhte hain goya ke tum is ki khoj mein lagey hue ho kaho"" is ka ilm to sirf Allah ko hai magar aksar log is haqeeqat se na waaqif hain """
  7,188,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho"" mein apni zaat ke liye kisi naffa aur nuqsaan ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhta, Allah hi jo kuch chahta hai woh ho taa hai aur agar mujhe ghaib ka ilm hota to mein bohat se faiday apne liye haasil kar laita aur mujhe kabhi koi nuqsaan nah pohanchana mein to mehez aik khabardaar karne wala aur khush khaberi sunanay wala hon unn logon ke liye jo meri baat manen """
  7,189,"woh Allah hi hai jis ne tumhe aik jaan se peda kya aur isi ki jins se is ka jora banaya taakay is ke paas sukoon haasil kere phir jab mard ne aurat ko dhaank liya to usay aik khafeef sa hamal reh gaya jisay liye liye woh chalti phurti rahi phir jab woh boujhal ho gayi to dono ne mil kar Allah , apne rab se dua ki ke agar to ne hum ko acha sa bacha diya to hum tairay shukar guzaar hon ge"
  7,190,magar jab Allah ne un ko aik sahih o salim bacha day diya to woh is ki iss bakhshish o inayat mein dosaron ko is ka shareektehraنے lagey Allah bohat buland o bartar hai un mushrikana baton se jo yeh log karte hain
  7,191,kaisay nadaan hain yeh log ke unn ko khuda ka shareektehra-tayhain jo kisi cheez ko bhi peda nahi karte balkay khud peda kiye jatay hain
  7,192,jo nah un ki madad kar satke hain aur nah aap apni madad hi par Qadir hain
  7,193,"agar tum inhen seedhi raah par anay ki dawat do to woh tumahray peechay nah ayen, tum khuwa inhen poukaro ya khamosh raho, dono sooraton mein tumahray liye yaksaa hi rahay"
  7,194,"tum log khuda ko chore kar jinhein pkarte ho woh to mehez bande hain jaisay tum bande ho un se duayen maang dekho, yeh tumhari duaon ka jawab den agar un ke baray mein tumahray khayalat sahih hain"
  7,195,"kya yeh paon rakhtay hain ke un se chalein? kya yeh haath rakhtay hain ke un se pakren? kya yeh ankhen rakhtay hain ke un se dekhen? kya yeh kaan rakhtay hain ke un se sunen? ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho ke"" bulaa lau apne tehra-ay hue sharikon ko phir tum sab mil kar mere khilaaf tadbeerye karo aur mujhe hargiz mohlat nah do"
  7,196,mera haami o nasir woh khuda hai jis ne yeh kitaab nazil ki hai aur woh naik admion ki himayat karta hai
  7,197,bakhilaf iss ke tum jinhein khuda ko chore kar pkarte ho woh nah tumhari madad kar saktay hain aur nah khud apni madad hi karne ke qabil hain
  7,198,"balkay agar tum inhen seedhi raah par anay ke liye kaho to woh tumhari baat sun bhi nahi satke bzahir tum ko aisa nazar aata hai ke woh tumhari taraf dekh rahay hain magar fi al waqea woh kuch bhi nahi dekhte """
  7,199,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, narmi o dar guzar ka tareeqa ikhtiyar karo, Maroof ki Talqeen kiye jao, aur jahilon se nah uljho"
  7,200,"agar kabhi shetan tumhe aksaye to Allah ki panah mango, woh sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai"
  7,201,haqeeqat mein jo lau g mut-taqi hain unn ka haal to yeh hota hai ke kabhi shetan ke assar se koi bura khayaal agar inhen chhoo bhi jata hai to woh foran chokannay ho jatay hain aur phir inhen saaf nazar anay lagta hai ke un ke liye sahih tareeq car kya hai
  7,202,"rahay un ke ( yani shyatin ke ) bhai band, to woh inhen un ki kaj rawi mein kheinchain liye chalay jatay hain aur inhen bhataknay mein koi kasar utha nahi rakhtay"
  7,203,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jab tum inn logon ke samnay koi nishani ( yani moujza ) paish nahi karte to yeh kehte hain ke tum ne apne liye koi nishani kyun nah intikhab kar li? un se kaho"" mein to sirf uss wahi ki pairwi karta hon jo mere rab ne meri taraf bhaije hai yeh baseerat ki roshniyan hain tumahray rab ki taraf se aur hadaayat aur rehmat hai unn logon ke liye jo isay qubool karen"
  7,204,"jab quran tumahray samnay parha jaye to usay tavajja se suno aur khamosh raho, shayad ke tum par bhi rehmat ho jaye """
  7,205,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab ko subah o shaam yaad kya karo dil hi dil mein zaari aur khauf ke sath aur zabaan se bhi halki aawaz ke sath tum un logon mein se nah ho jao jo ghaflat mein parre hue hain"
  7,206,"jo farishtay tumahray rab ke huzoor taqarab ka maqam rakhtay hain woh kabhi apni barayi ke ghamand mein aa kar is ki ibadat se mun nahi morty aur is ki tasbeeh karte hain, aur is ke agay jhuke rehtay hain"
